description: move a dataset in seismic store
help:
> python sdutil mv *sdpath_from *sdpath_to (options)
  move a dataset to a different location in seismic store (same tenant required)
  *sdpath_from  : the origin seismic store path. sd://<tenant>/<subproject>/<path>/<dataset>
  *sdpath_to    : the destiantion seismic store path. sd://<tenant>/<subproject>/<path>*/<dataset>
  (options)      | --idtoken=<token> pass the credential token to use, rather than generating a new one
name: mv
